# CreativeDev Cursor Rules

- Always follow AGENTS.md
- Ask before creating new folders
- Max 15 components
- Server components by default
- Use early returns
- No nested ternaries
- No `any` types
- Tailwind for styling
- Use Hero, CTA, and Testimonials sections as defined
- WhatsApp links must use generateWhatsAppLink utility
- Testimonial names must be real African names; avatars must reflect this
- Optimize images for web
- Validate responsive design on mobile